OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start.
OL,6,FCloud will increase this morning, with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,8,Freaching the Peak District by early
OL,9,Fafternoon and then gradually spreading
OL,10,Feast to all areas by early evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain this evening, clearing
OL,13,Feast by the early hours. Large amounts
OL,14,Fof cloud and showers or longer spells
OL,15,Fof rain will follow, perhaps locally
OL,16,Fheavy. Becoming dry and clear later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
